<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17490222-41">
               <interp inst="t17490222-41" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17490222-41" type="year" value="1749"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17490222-41" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17490222"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17490222-41" type="date" value="17490222"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17490222-41-off194-c190" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-defend270 t17490222-41-off194 t17490222-41-verdict197"></join>
         
               <p>208. 
               
                  <persName id="t17490222-41-defend270" type="defendantName">
                     Robert 
                     Sherwood , alias <rs id="t17490222-41-alias-2" type="alias">
                        <join result="nameAlias" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-defend270 t17490222-41-alias-2"></join>Harwood</rs>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-defend270" type="surname" value="Sherwood"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-defend270" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-defend270" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17490222-41-off194" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-off194" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-off194" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing twenty-eight pounds of butter, value 12 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17490222-41-victim272" type="victimName">
                     Steven 
                     Flower 
                  <interp inst="t17490222-41-victim272" type="surname" value="Flower"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-victim272" type="given" value="Steven"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-victim272" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-off194 t17490222-41-victim272"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            . <rs id="t17490222-41-cd195" type="crimeDate">Jan. 27</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-off194 t17490222-41-cd195"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17490222-41-person273">
                  Steven 
                  Flower 
               <interp inst="t17490222-41-person273" type="surname" value="Flower"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-person273" type="given" value="Steven"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-person273" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The Prisoner took away half a firkin of butter out of my shop. I did not see him take it .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17490222-41-person274">
                  Thomas 
                  Sumeroise 
               <interp inst="t17490222-41-person274" type="surname" value="Sumeroise"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-person274" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-person274" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             . I am a servant to Mr. Flower. On the 27th of January last two persons came into our shop, and asked for a pennyworth of cheese; my master is a <rs id="t17490222-41-viclabel196" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-victim272 t17490222-41-viclabel196"></join> . While I was serving them, a third person slipp'd in, and stole half a firkin of butter ; he was got about eight doors from the shop door; I ran after him, and took him with it upon his head.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17490222-41-verdict197" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-verdict197" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs> of felony.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17490222-41-punish198" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17490222-41-punish198" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17490222-41-defend270 t17490222-41-punish198"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
